    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>For joining two narrow boards. Both boards are planed smooth, coated with glue, and rubbed together until all air pockets and excess glue are expelled from the joint. No clamping is necessary and the joint is extremely strong.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000027101/Smit, Means Illustrated Construction Dictionary (1985)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Para unir dos tablas angostas. Ambas tablas están cepilladas uniformemente, cubiertas con goma, y frotadas juntas hasta que todo los bolsos de aire y exceso de goma sea expelido de la junta. No es necesario sujetarlos con abrazaderas y la junta es extremadamente fuerte.
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor het samenvoegen van twee smalle planken, waarbij beide planken glad zijn geschaafd, met lijm ingesmeerd en net zolang tegen elkaar gewreven tot alle luchtbellen en overtollige lijmresten uit de voeg zijn verdwenen. Klampen is niet nodig en de verbinding is bijzonder stevig.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>用來連結兩塊窄板的接點。兩塊板子均刨成平滑、覆塗黏著劑，並相互摩擦至所有氣穴與多餘的黏著劑自該接點排出。此種接點不需以夾鉗固定，極為堅固。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
